1.0: (2001/06/27)
	- Added index file format JJDX, which can be used instead of
	  XJDX index files. JGloss will create the index if none is
	  found.
	- Added command line option for JJDX creation and opening
	  JGloss files.
	- Speeded up initial display of documents. Unfortunately,
	  it is still too slow.
        - Hidden annotations are not longer expanded after a document
	  is loaded.
0.9 (2001/06/14):
	- Initial release.